## `components/` hard-delete (2026-07-11)

- Entire `components/` **directory removed**.
- **Do not** recreate `components/` or `git checkout` the whole tree. Named migrates only: `features/operator/`, `features/auth/studio/`, `features/account/`. New UI → `features/` or `components-V2/` per [`doc/frontend/02-folder-map.md`](doc/frontend/02-folder-map.md).

## Operator / account rebuild noise bans

- No Guardian / PA / owl / brand `public/` restore in these phases
- No AdminCN demo prune or `platform-fake-db` product wiring
- No new REST for dashboard/account reads
- No cross-phase route restores mixed into the same PR (join / client / playground / trade stay closed)

